spec_data.Name: writerperfect
spec_data.Description:
writerperfect is a collection of command-line tools to transform various document
formats into ODF. Among supported input formats are:
* AbiWord
* Adobe PageMaker
* Apple Keynote
* Corel WordPerfect
* CorelDRAW
* Microsoft Publisher
* Microsoft Visio
* Microsoft Works
